description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic nurse to join the CHD and Heart Failure service. The service operates across County Durham &amp; Darlington caring for people in hospital, clinics and their own homes. The successful candidates will be able to demonstrate knowledge and experience of working with coronary heart disease and heart failure patients and be able to work independently as well as part of a team. Applicants should be capable of independent travel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;*This band 5 developmental post is a role available to offer an opportunity for someone who has a keen interest and experience in cardiology but may not possess a cardiology related course. Once these qualifications are attained the individual will meet the gateway to practice as a Band 6 Practitioner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
